<collectingCountry box="[469,536,1981,2005]" name="Egypt" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Egypt</collectingCountry>
and Abyssinian [= Eritrean] coast; restricted to Tor by 
<bibRefCitation author="Mertens, R." box="[1157,1334,1980,2005]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" pagination="1 - 106" refId="ref58796" refString="Mertens, R. (1967) Die herpetologische Sektion des Natur-Museums und Forschungs-Institutes Senckenberg in Frankfurt a. M. nebst einem Verzeichnis ihrer Typen. Senckenbergiana Biologica, 48, 1 - 106." type="journal article" year="1967">Mertens (1967)</bibRefCitation>
